snippet.title: COCOON - Release Date Trailer - Nintendo Switch
snippet.description:
COCOON is coming to Nintendo Switch on September 29, 2023!

COCOON is a unique puzzle adventure game in which each world exists as an orb you carry on your back. Leap between worlds, journey through diverse biomes, and face monstrous guardians to unravel a cosmic mystery! 

#NintendoSwitch #COCOON
